      FRESA CHATBOT FOR MULTIPLE TABLE ANALYSIS AND ANSWERING 

1. TECHNOLOGIES USED
     
       python 3.13.7
       Visual Studio Code

2. CREATE VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT 
  
         step 1: open vs code and open project folder
         step 2: open terminal in vs code
         step 3: create virtual environment using command "python -m venv venv"
         step 4: activate virtual environment using command "venv\Scripts\activate"

3. INSTALL REQUIRED PACKAGES AND RUN THE APPLICATION
         step 1: install required packages using command "pip install -r requirements.txt"

4. HOW TO RUN THE APPLICATION
         step 1: run the application using command "uvicorn main:app --reload"
         step 2: open browser and go to "http://127.0.0.1:8000/"

5. HOW TO RUN IN POSTMAN
         step 1: open postman
         step 2: Get Data
            Method: Get
            URL:  http://127.0.0.1:8000/get_data
        step 3: Query Data
            Method: Post
            URL:  http://127.0.0.1:8000/query
            Body → raw → JSON:

            {
                "dataset": "shipments",
                "query": "give shipment details where status=pending",
                "chart_type": "bar"
            }